RANGE_BEGIN 0 100
	ADDRESS 1.2.3.6
ENTRY_BEGIN
MATCH opcode qtype qname
ADJUST copy_id
REPLY QR AA NOERROR
SECTION QUESTION
www.example.test. IN A
SECTION ANSWER
www.example.test. IN A 10.20.30.66
