STEP 1 QUERY
ENTRY_BEGIN
REPLY RD DO
SECTION QUESTION
www.example.test. IN A
ENTRY_END

STEP 10 CHECK_ANSWER
ENTRY_BEGIN
MATCH all
REPLY QR RD RA DO SERVFAIL
SECTION QUESTION
www.example.test. IN A
SECTION ANSWER
ENTRY_END

; to resolve pending lookups
STEP 20 TRAFFIC
SCENARIO_END
